description	"Jyn Erso

Class: Hero
Brief Overview: 
A speedy pistoleer with advanced movement capabilities and a shocking/displacing sidearm.

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
- Jyn's Truncheon
-- Based on Lightsaber
-- Dual style
-- Cannot block blasters/sabers
-- 35% less damage
-- 30% shorter range
-- 33% thinner radius
- A180 Blaster Pistol
-- Based on WESTAR-34 (2)
-- 10% more FP damage
-- 10% faster reload
- A180 Ion Attachment
-- Based on Bowcaster (3)
-- Electrocutes and knocks back/down targets
-- 150% more FP damage
-- 50% slower reload
-- 15% slower movement
- Sonic Detonators (2)

^6Inventory:
- Electrobinoculars ^3[CS3]
- Portable Assault Sentry ^3[CS4]

^8Attributes:
- Combat Training (Force Jump 1)
- Dexterity (2)
- Healing (3)
- Invisible to Force Sense

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (3) ^3[CS1]
- Dash (2) ^3[CS2]
- Flipkick (2) ^3[Single/double-jump off players ^3& surfaces ^3sideways/forwards]

Jyn Erso was a Human female soldier and former criminal, who became a pivotal member of the Alliance to Restore the Republic when she led Rogue One in stealing the Death Star plans during the Battle of Scarif."